  note = {Radosevich and Halloran (2025) audit security vulnerabilities in Anthropic's Model Context Protocol (MCP), which allows LLMs to integrate with external tools and data sources. The authors demonstrate that language models using MCP can be manipulated through prompt injection to execute malicious code, enable remote access, and steal credentials},
